text: Great authentic food at a great price! Will come by often from the east to have my weekly fix. Will always have the chicken rice. Chicken is tasty and juicy. Chilli is not too spicy but does the job. Many other dishes to try. One of the best Halal options in Taman Jurong. A must have!

Highly recommend! If you're seeing this, it's a sign to go and check them out. The vendors are such nice and friendly people. (: They give fairly big portions for whatever you order so you can eat until you shiok. It's may be simple looking but it's so delicious and at this price point, super worth it.
Food is great and cheap with generous portions. Worth trying it out and nice service from the vendors.
Authentic Malay food that I tried on the recent times. Can feel the old style cooking. Fried rice with ayam sambal is recomnneded.
The chicken Rice Is Really Awesome.. feel like eating it at Home.. Especially The Chili.This Is Really The Real chilli For Chicken Rice.. Must Try..üëçüëç
